plots of data from netCDF, HDF, and GRIB datasets. Although
its strength is in making longitude-latitude (map) plots,

including keograms and Hovmoeller diagrams; general 2D color
plots; and line plots. Data arrays may be "sliced" from larger
multidimensional arrays (aka, variables). A large selection
of global map projections is available for lon-lat figures.
